name: Flatlanders in "Circle of blinking eyes"
description:
This mint features the Flatlanders in an ancient ritual dance the do to summon those from the dimension from above (us). Give them a poke to let them know you're there and transform their lives forever

For the devlog and artist notes, see my notion: https://pixelmoar.com/Circle-of-blinking-eyes-0d838275c02e44b195a28fd961944c35
